            <![CDATA[
            <h3>Version 2.0.15 - LMSGetValue Interception for Navigation</h3>

            <h4>New Approach</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>Uses sessionStorage to store pending navigation before reload</li>
                <li>Intercepts LMSGetValue/GetValue to return modified suspend_data</li>
                <li>Modifies "l" field (last slide position) in decompressed data</li>
                <li>Cleaner approach - intercepts BEFORE content initializes</li>
            </ul>

            <h4>How It Works</h4>
            <ul>
                <li>1. Store target slide in sessionStorage</li>
                <li>2. Reload SCORM content iframe</li>
                <li>3. LMSGetValue interceptor returns modified suspend_data</li>
                <li>4. Content initializes to the target slide</li>
            </ul>

